targets.rawSql:
SELECT COUNT(*)
FROM servers
WHERE service_name = '$service'
/* AND ($subservices = 'all' OR  subservice_name IN ($subservices)); */

options.content: ### All servers where at least one service VM is running on

list.definition: select subservice_name from subservices where service_name= '$service';
list.name: subservices
list.query: select subservice_name from subservices where service_name= '$service';

list.definition:
SELECT string_agg(server_name_transformed, '|')
FROM (
  SELECT LOWER(server_name) || '.ad001.siemens.net' AS server_name_transformed
  FROM servers
  WHERE service_name = '$service'  
  UNION ALL
  
  SELECT UPPER(server_name) || '.ad001.siemens.net' AS server_name_transformed
  FROM servers
  WHERE service_name = '$service'
) AS combined_results;
